      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and provides enough power for standard commuting, though you may notice some typical engine noise associated with its age. The transmission shifts through all gears, though it lacks the crispness of a newer model. Visually, the exterior shows its history with several minor scuffs, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible thinning in high-traffic areas like the driver's seat, and the plastic trim has some scratches. It has been maintained regularly to keep it roadworthy, making it a solid choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
