    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been well-loved and is still in great shape, running super smooth and ready for all your weekend adventures. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
