      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a driver-focused E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power unit is paired with a 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring a pure analog connection to the tarmac. The vehicle features Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a forged aluminum multi-link rear suspension for precise lateral dynamics. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed as preventative measures, ensuring the structural integrity of the high-compression internals. While the paintwork shows minor stone chipping consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain remains in peak synchronization, delivering its 414 hp linear surge all the way to the 8,400 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
