    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between premium performance and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, glossy finish, though closer inspection reveals the expected minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up chip on the passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all electronic features\u2014from the navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been consistently cared for, with a service history that manifests in its smooth gear shifts and responsive handling. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It is a clean, reliable, and well-presented example that is ready for its next owner to drive away with complete confidence.",
