      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs great, looks sharp, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! I've taken good care of it and I'm sure you'll love how it drives. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat and help you get behind the wheel!",
